    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Ituglanis paraguassuensis, holotype, 41.2 mm SL, LIRP 5780." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176687/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176688>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dorsal view of neurocranium and upper jaw and associated structures of I. paraguassuensis. AOR – antorbital; APA – autopalatine; EPE - epioccipital; FPR – parietal fontanel; FSO – postparieto-supraoccipital fontanel; GBC – swim bladder; i 1 - i 3, i 10 - i 11 – infraorbital pores; ll 1 – lateral line pore; MAX – maxilla; MET - mesethmoid; PAR – parietal; PMX - premaxilla; po 1 – preopercular pores; PP-SO – postparieto-supraoccipital; PTE - pterotic; PTT-SCL – postemporo- supracleithrum; s 1 - s 6 – supraorbital pores; SPH - sphenotic; STB – supraorbital tendon bone; VCU – vertebral centrum; VOM - vomer." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176688/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176689>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Lateral view of the left suspensorium and opercular apparatus of I. paraguassuensis. HYO - hyomandibula; INT - interopercle; MTG - metapterygoid; OPC - opercle; PPC - preopercle; QDT - quadrate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176689/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

